{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"28":"Foods (Kitab Al-At'imah)"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3786,"arabicnumber":3786,"text":"حدثنا ابن المثنى، حدثني أبو عامر، حدثنا هشام، عن قتادة، عن عكرمة، عن ابن عباس، أن النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم نهى عن لبن الجلالة ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":28,"hadith":51}}]}